>> source: https://www.bluezones.com/recipe/hearts-of-palm-ceviche/

Combine @hearts of palm{1%cup}, @sweet onion{1%small}, @sweet red peppers{2%small}, @habanero pepper{1/4%small}, and @cilantro{1%Tbsp} in a #bowl{}, drizzle with @lime juice{2}, and add @salt{1%tsp}; toss to combine.

Season with @pepper{}, if desired, and serve immediately. Enjoy alone or served with popcorn, plantain chips, or tortilla chips.
